</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No actions are required unless the print quality is out of specification</b>.
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-1EF80D24-6A70-49D8-B1E7-EC23A04F2946" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><?xm-replace_text Prevent personal injury (Start with a simple command (Do not ..) and describe the possible risk).?>
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This error is generated during the calibration step: "PrintheadWaveforms" which is part of the printhead calibration sequence.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
